Checklist for a new release:

[ ] All developer documentation current and double-checked for accuracy
[ ] User documentation updated to reflect changes in user interface
[ ] Passes test suite (not implemented yet)
[ ] Known bugs documented
[ ] All issues fixed by this release updated on Tracker
[ ] Updated Version numbering in and out of main document
[ ] Build system tested on Chez and Petite
[ ] Updated ChangeLog
[ ] Binaries released
[ ] Website updated
[ ] Announce to lists and newsgroups
[ ] Post on Blog
